Revision history for Perl extension Text::Tabulate

1.1.1 22 Jan 2008
	- keyword 'our' didn't exist until Perl 5.6. Require at least
	  this version of Perl. Otherwise it fails testing.

1.1 Jan 2008
	- added 'joint' option for use when format and tabulate are
	  used in a string context.

1.0 July 2007
	- Turned into a module.

0.5  2000s
	- Initial creation as a utility script.

